name: CityGripe
0:
”Alexa, tell City Gripe I'm sick of my commute because it is too long.”
”I absolutely can't stand my relationship.”
”I don't like the weather”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: city gripe
des: City Gripe allows users to complain to Alexa about various things in there life including their love life, commute, or the weather. Using Department of Commerce open data, Alexa will either try and suggest somewhere the user could move or will tell the user of an ever worse of county. Winner of "Best use of Commerce Data" at the U.S. Department of Commerce Open Data Alexa Hackathon.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
